contents: <sup>1</sup>There is more value in real-world experience than there is sitting in a classroom. <sup>2</sup>I’ve learned a lot from working in a restaurant. <sup>3</sup>I plan to run my own restaurant one day. <sup>4</sup>I learned math by figuring out checks and calculating tax. <sup>5</sup>I learned communication skills by conversing with customers and co-workers.
